==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Proll
<hw>Proll</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To prowl about; to rob.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Though ye <qex>prolle</qex> aye, ye shall it never find.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Proller</ent>⟦br⟧
